### 1. 健康检查
GET http://localhost:8080/ping
Accept: application/json

###

### 2. 生成试题 (范围筛选)
# 获取 5 道 "Mathematics" 题目
# 难度范围: "A" 到 "C" (包含 A, B, C)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/generate-quiz
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "subject": "Mathematics",
  "difficulty_start": "A",
  "difficulty_end": "C",
  "limit": 5,
  "chapters": [
    "高等数学",
    "计组"
  ]
}

###

### 3. 生成试题 (单难度筛选)
# 难度范围: "C" 到 "C" (只选 C)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/generate-quiz
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "subject": "Mathematics",
  "difficulty_start": "C",
  "difficulty_end": "C",
  "limit": 5
}